Package fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.interfaces Description

Interfaces for DEVS simulation models.

This package provides two sets of interfaces defining operations used at different time with DEVS models. A first set defines the operations used on atomic and coupled models at simulation execution time. The second set are interfaces for model factories used at simulation architecture description and instantiation time as facilities to create instances of atomic and coupled models in the composition process leading to a run time simulation architecture.
